usage_guide.title: Usage Instructions
usage_guide.point_1: 1. Databases can be associated with Q&A robots to extract information from conversations and store it in specified data tables, or use existing data in the tables to respond to user inquiries. Please create a knowledge base before creating a robot, then associate it in the robot settings.
usage_guide.point_2: 2. Supports importing existing data via Excel templates and JSON templates, and also supports exporting stored data to Excel files.

message.no_edit_permission: You do not have permission to edit this database
message.no_delete_permission: You do not have permission to delete this database

delete_confirm.title: Delete Confirmation
delete_confirm.content: After deleting the data table, all data in the table will be deleted and cannot be recovered. Are you sure you want to delete the data table {name}?
